{"tid":1434214,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中伏！八五罷工完全冇人講！","createTime":"2019-08-08T16:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:06:31.000Z","uid":33966,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e02f4e896753aa3f2c2b0b65b09e4d0c7b6ac06","tid":1434214,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:53:00.000Z","msg":"原本大家用好多心機心力去宣傳八月五日三罷，希望引起好大迴響，以作出進一步嘅三罷行動。但係唔知係有意定無意，嗰日嘅警民衝突就完全轉移咗焦點！而家個個都只係討論警犬記者會同埋鐳射筆。真正對政府最大威脅嘅三罷完全冇人講。完全冇總結到究竟嗰日有幾多人罷工，有幾大影響。認真而家有幾多人仲記得幾日前係搞過罷工？係冇啊！時間愈耐件事愈丟淡，咁以後仲點搞三罷啊？！大家唔好唔記得八五嘅重點係三罷啊！"},{"pid":"a6c493c86f5490dcf77741d5e5c1a3499a1a6c86","tid":1434214,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7faeb5de558e6d9a3715458663c76904e2903eb","tid":1434214,"uid":266011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb5c74d88900da4e5eb4809198c2fc2e4b52ee7","tid":1434214,"uid":266011,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tiNO0U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tiNO0U.png&h=09340a3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40747965f2fd2151d3ed2ec9176e6c194d9fb62b","tid":1434214,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f4adf93db30730ff696c5f3f1b92f722d28